                                    <h3 class="card-text tx-teal ">1. INTRODUCTION AND GENERAL TERMS</h3>
                                    <p>These terms apply to the use of website and other products/tools developed by GoTSkillZ.</p>
                                    <p><em>If you have any questions or comments about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at&nbsp;</em><a href="mailto:contact@gotskillz.gg"><em>contact@gotskillz.gg</em></a>.</p>
