                                    <p>This Privacy Policy should be read in conjunction with our terms of use for the Website and any terms applied to any of the services/tools.</p>
                                    <p>The Online Services may contain hyperlinks to services owned and operated by third parties, on enable the Online Services to be connected to those services by other means. Third party services may have their own privacy policies and we recommend that you review them. They may govern the use of personal information that you submit, or which is collected by cookies and other tracking technologies whilst using these services. We do not accept any responsibility or liability for the privacy practices of such third-party services and your use of these services is at your own risk.</p>
                                    <p>We may make changes to this Privacy Policy in future, which will be notified to you.</p>
                                    <hr class="bd-white-1">
                                    <h3 class="card-text tx-teal ">2. INFORMATION WE MAY COLLECT ABOUT YOU</h3>
                                    <p>We collect and process the following information which may include your personal data.</p>
                                    <p><strong>INFORMATION PROVIDED WHEN YOU REGISTER WITH OUR ONLINE SERVICES (&ldquo;REGISTRATION INFORMATION&rdquo;)</strong></p>
                                    <p>In order to access restricted sections of the Website, you are required to providing the following information: (*required)</p>
                                    <ul>
                                        <li>First Name*;</li>
                                        <li>Last Name*; and</li>
                                        <li>Email*;</li>
                                    </ul>
                                    <p>When you sign up or login to our Online Services, we may collect the following information:</p>
                                    <ul>
                                        <li>Type of device used;</li>
                                        <li>IP address;</li>
                                        <li>Geolocation details including region, country, state, city;</li>
                                        <li>Type of browser used; and</li>
                                        <li>Identifiers associated with your devices.</li>
                                    </ul>
                                    <p><strong>OPTIONAL INFORMATION PROVIDED BY YOU WHEN USING THE ONLINE SERVICES (&ldquo;OPTIONAL INFORMATION&rdquo;)</strong></p>
                                    <p>If you wish, following registration you may add the following information to your GoTSKillZ profile, by using your GoTSkillZ account settings:</p>
                                    <ul>
                                        <li>Full address;</li>
                                        <li>Phone number;</li>
                                        <li>Avatar picture;</li>
                                        <li>Twitch account;</li>
                                        <li>Facebook profile;</li>
                                        <li>FaceIT profile;</li>
                                        <li>Sostronk profile;</li>
                                        <li>Instagram Profile;</li>
                                        <li>Twitter profile;</li>
                                        <li>YouTube profile;</li>
                                        <li>Discord profile; and</li>
                                        <li>Google profile.</li>
                                    </ul>
                                    <p>You are also able to connect your GoTSkillZ account to third party platforms like FaceIt, Steam, YouTube, in which case we collect the following information in respect of each third-party platform:</p>
                                    <ul>
                                        <li>Username/nickname</li>
                                        <li>User ID</li>
                                        <li>An access token, to allow us to connect to your third-party account and to ensure we are connecting to the correct third-party account; and</li>
                                        <li>A refresh token, which allows us to request additional access tokens, and therefore re-connect to third party accounts, until the refresh token is withdrawn (if, for example, you decide to disconnect your account from the third-party platform).</li>
                                    </ul>
                                    <p>If you choose to link a platform to your GoTSkillZ account, we will collect the following information in respect of each game:</p>
                                    <ul>
                                        <li>Nickname;</li>
                                        <li>ID;</li>
                                        <li>Rank/Skill Level/Elo, which is based on your previous performance in games;</li>
                                        <li>Basic profile statistics;</li>
                                        <li>Bans information;</li>
                                    </ul>
