                                        <li>Match results;</li>
                                    </ul>
                                    <ul>
                                        <li>Event logs, which relate to your in-game behavior;</li>
                                    </ul>
                                    <p><strong>INFORMATION USED TO UNDERSTAND HOW USERS HAVE FOUND OUR ONLINE SERVICES (&ldquo;ATTRIBUTION INFORMATION&rdquo;)</strong></p>
                                    <p>When you sign up, we record the web page from which you have accessed GoTSkillZ.GG.</p>
                                    <p><strong>CONTACT INFORMATION PROVIDED BY YOU WHEN YOU CONTACT US OR USE THE SUPPORT CENTRE (&ldquo;CONTACT INFORMATION&rdquo;)</strong></p>
                                    <p>We may ask you for, or you may submit, certain contact information to us whenever you contact us through the Support Centre.</p>
