                                    <p><strong>CONTACT INFORMATION PROVIDED BY YOU WHEN YOU SIGN UP TO OUR MAILING LIST (&ldquo;MAILING LIST INFORMATION&rdquo;)</strong></p>
                                    <p>We may ask you for, or you may submit, certain contact information to us whenever you sign up to our Mailing List.</p>
                                    <p>This may include:</p>
