                                    <h3 class="card-text tx-teal ">3. WHY WE COLLECT INFORMATION ABOUT YOU</h3>
                                    <p><strong>TO PROVIDE THE ONLINE SERVICES TO YOU</strong></p>
                                    <p>We will use information about you (including Basic Information, Registration Information, Optional Information, Analytics and User Content) for delivering our Online Services to you under the terms of use agreed between us. The processing of information in this way is necessary for us to analyze performance based on game data, and to ensure the tools/services deliver the features promised and function properly, so that you have the best experience.</p>
                                    <p><strong>TO HELP US IMPROVE THE ONLINE SERVICES AND FIX ANY PROBLEMS</strong></p>
                                    <p>We may process information about you (including Basic Information, User Content, Registration Information and Analytics) so that we can analyze and improve our Online Services.</p>
                                    <p>This processing is also necessary for us to pursue our legitimate interests of (i) ensuring that our Online Services function properly so that you and other users have the best experience using our Online Services; (ii) improving the quality of our Online Services, and providing a better experience to our users; and (iii) identifying and correcting any bugs in &nbsp;our Online Services.</p>
                                    <p>We use Google Analytics to help us understand how our Online services are used.</p>
                                    <p><strong>TO RESPOND TO YOUR ENQUIRIES AND REQUESTS FOR SUPPORT AND TO ENABLE YOU TO USE SUPPORT CENTRE</strong></p>
                                    <p>We may process Contact Information so that we are able to properly respond to your enquiries</p>
                                    <p>We use <a href="mailto:contact@gotskillz.gg"><em>contact@gotskillz.gg</em></a> to help us handle requests for support.</p>
