                                    <h3 class="card-text tx-teal ">4. COOKIES</h3>
                                    <p>A cookie is a text file placed onto your device when you access our Online Services. We use cookies and other online tracking devices such as web beacons, and flash object storage to deliver, improve and monitor our Website and Clients, including in the following ways:</p>
