                                        <li>the personal data was unlawfully processed;</li>
                                        <li>you need the personal data to be deleted in order to comply with legal obligations;</li>
                                        <li>the personal data is processed in relation to the offer of a service to a child.</li>
                                    </ul>
                                    <p><strong>OBTAIN A MACHINE-READABLE COPY OF YOUR PERSONAL DATA, WHICH YOU CAN USE WITH ANOTHER SERVICE PROVIDER</strong></p>
                                    <p>If we are processing data in order to perform our obligations to you, or because you consented, or if that processing is carried out by automated means, we will help you to move, copy or transfer your personal data to other IT systems.</p>
                                    <p>If you request, we will supply you with the relevant personal data in a commonly used, machine-readable and interoperable format. Where it is technically feasible, you can ask us to send this information directly to another IT system provider if you prefer.</p>
